  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2>Seek refuge underground before the apocalypse strikes, and survive a world without oxygen by using genetically modified plants. Can you get them all before it’s too late?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/f2928ae5107b094f48d0c6add40cd8a7.poster.avif?t=1696659963\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/f2928ae5107b094f48d0c6add40cd8a7.webm?t=1696659963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/f2928ae5107b094f48d0c6add40cd8a7.mp4?t=1696659963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build</h2>Create tools, collect resources and build a shelter. This will be your new home.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/d6eb957e82d72ad5e30fef4c7270002e.poster.avif?t=1696659963\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/d6eb957e82d72ad5e30fef4c7270002e.webm?t=1696659963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/d6eb957e82d72ad5e30fef4c7270002e.mp4?t=1696659963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight</h2>Defend yourself from those corrupted by famine and loneliness. Loot to survive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/78f8d31f7fc02ab7ebbc5ba91e0b7d42.poster.avif?t=1696659963\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/78f8d31f7fc02ab7ebbc5ba91e0b7d42.webm?t=1696659963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230000/extras/78f8d31f7fc02ab7ebbc5ba91e0b7d42.mp4?t=1696659963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Single player PVE sandbox experience.<br></li><li> Crafting mechanics, workstations.<br></li><li> Dynamic base building.<br></li><li> Weapons and tools system.<br></li><li> Extraction and refining of resources.<br></li><li> Enemies.<br></li><li> Agriculture.<br></li><li> Food cooking mechanics. <br></li><li> Day-night cycle. <br></li><li> Character state mechanics.<br></li><li> Oxygen system.<br></li><li> Procedural generation map and resources.</li></ul>",
